        <h1>AI in Fundraising: How Artificial Intelligence Is Changing Nonprofit Giving</h1>
        <div class="art-meta">
            <span>April 9, 2026</span>
            <span class="art-meta-dot"></span>
            <span>11 min read</span>
        </div>
    </div>
